<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">佛說大報父母恩重經</sent>
<sent type="title" lang="kor" page="01a" n="1">부모의 은 갑 이라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">如是我聞 一時 佛在王舍城 </sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="2">일시예 부톄 샤의</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">闍衛國 袛樹給孤獨園 與大比丘三萬八千人 菩薩摩訶薩衆</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">뎨 삼만팔쳔 리고 겨시더니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="4">尒時 世尊將領大衆</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="4">대을 솔샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="5">往詣南行</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="5">남녀고로 가시다가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="6">見一堆枯骨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="6">사  보시고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="7">尒時 如來 五體投地 禮拜枯骨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a" n="7">절시거</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a-01b" n="8">阿難大衆白佛言</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01a-01b" n="8">아란과 대이 부텨 오</sent><!--란^과-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">世尊如來是三界大師 四生慈父</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">셰존하 삼계예 스이시고 의 아비시니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">衆人歸敬</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">사미 다 거든</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">云何禮拜枯骨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">엇뎨  보고 절시니잇고</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">佛告阿難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02a" n="1">부톄 아란려 니샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02a" n="2">汝雖是吾上足弟子</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02a" n="2">네 비록 나의 읏듬 뎨오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02a" n="3">出家深遠</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02a" n="3">집 나건 디 오라도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02a" n="4">知事未廣</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02a" n="4">이 모도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02a" n="5">此一堆枯骨 或是我前世翁祖 累世爺嬢 吾今禮拜</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02a" n="5">이  젼의 나의 하나비어나 부뫼어나  절노라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">佛告阿難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">부톄 아란려 니샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">汝將此一堆枯骨 分作二分</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">네 이  둘희 호라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">若是男子骨頭 白了又重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">남의  희오 므겁고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">若是女子骨頭 黑了又輕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="4">녀이  검고 가븨여우니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="5">阿難白佛言</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="5">아라니 오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="6">世尊 男人在世/</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="6">셰존하 남 이의 이실 제</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="7">衫帶靴帽裝裏</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="7">한삼 닙고  오 훠 신고 이실</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="8">卽知是男兒之身</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="8">남의 모민 줄 알오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="9">女人在世 濃塗赤硃臙脂 蘭麝裝裏</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="9">녀이 분 고 연지 딕고 샤 고 단여 이실</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b" n="10">卽知是女流之身</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b" n="10">녀이 모민 줄 알어니와</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="02b-03a" n="11">如今死後 白骨一般</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="02b-03a" n="11">이제 주근 후의  가지어든</sent><!--후^의-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">敎弟子如何認得</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">엇뎨 알리잇가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">佛告阿難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03a" n="2">부톄 아란려 니샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">若是男人 在世之時 入於伽藍 聽講誦經</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">남 사라실 졔 뎌가 도 닐그며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03a" n="4">禮拜三寶 念佛名字 所以骨頭 白了又重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03a" n="4">부텨도 저소오며 념불도   희오 므겁고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03a-03b" n="5">女人在世 恣情婬欲</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03a-03b" n="5">녀이 디 하 젼되오 미 음탐니</sent><!--되^오-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">生男養女 一廻生箇孩兒 流出三斗三勝凝血</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1"> 번 식 나호매 피 서 말 서 되 흐로고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">飮孃八斛四斗白乳 所以骨頭 黑了又輕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">아기도  져즐 여듧 셤 너 말 머그모로  검고 가븨여우니라</sent><!--여들ᄇ-->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="3">阿難聞語 痛割於心 垂淚悲泣 白佛言</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="3">아라니 매 셜워 울며 오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="4">世尊 母恩德者 云何報答</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="4">셰존하 어믜 은과 덕과 엇뎨 야 가리잇고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="5">佛告阿難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="5">부톄 아란려 니샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="6">如今諦聽</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="6">네 셰 드라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="7">吾今爲汝 分別解說</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="7">내 너희 위야 닐오리라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="03b" n="8">阿孃懷子 十月之中 極是辛苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="03b" n="8">어미 식 여 열  이예 신괴 그지업스니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">阿孃一箇月</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">어미 식 여  리면</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">懷胎恰如草頭上珠</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">회 플틔 이슬티</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">保朝不保暮</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">아 잇고 나죄 업스니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="4">早晨聚將來</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="4">새배 모닷다가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="5">午時消散去</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="5">나 스러디니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="6">阿孃兩箇月 懷胎恰如撲落凝蘇</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="6">두 리면 회 박낙여 얼읜 것 니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04a" n="7">阿孃三箇月 懷胎恰如凝血</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04a" n="7">석 리면 회 얼읜 피 니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">阿孃四箇月 懷胎稍作人形</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">넉 리면 회 졈졈 사 얼구리 이니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">阿孃五箇月 懷胎在孃腹中 生五胞 何者 名爲五胞 頭爲一胞 兩肘爲三胞 兩膝爲五胞</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04b" n="2">다 리면 회 머리와 두 엇게와 두 무룹과 이니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">阿孃六箇月 懷胎孩兒 在孃腹中 六精開 何者 名爲六精 眼爲一精 耳爲二精 鼻爲三精 口是四精 舌是五精 意爲六精</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">여 리면 회 아기 눈과 귀와 고와 입과 혀와 과 여니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">阿孃七箇月 懷胎孩兒 在孃腹中 生三百六十骨節 八萬四千毛孔</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">닐곱 리면 회 아기 삼여슌 와 팔만쳔 털굼기 나니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">阿孃八箇月 懷胎生其意智</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05a" n="2">여 리면 회 아기 과 디혜 나며</sent><!--여ᄇ-->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">長其九竅</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">아홈 가짓 굼기 기니라</sent><!-- ‘홈’은 ‘홉’의 오각으로 보임. -->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">阿孃九箇月 懷胎孩兒 在孃腹中 喫食</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">아홉 리면 회 아기  안셔 오식니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">不湌桃梨蒜菓 五穀飮味</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">복숑와  마 과실 먹디 말고 오곡 마 머그라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">阿孃生藏向下</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">어믜  안 장은 아래로 향엿고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="4">熟藏向上</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="4">사근 장은 우흐로 여 인 이예</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="5">有一座山 此山 有三般名字</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="5"> 뫼히 이시니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="6">一號須彌山</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="6">슈미산니라도 며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="7">二號業山</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="7">업산니라도 며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="8">三號血山</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="8">피뫼히라도 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="9">此山一度崩來</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="9">이 안뫼히라 이 뫼히 믈어디여</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="10">化爲一條凝血</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="10"> 들 피주리 되어</sent><!-- 쌍계사판에는 ‘들’이 아닌 ‘올’로 나옴. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="05b" n="11">流入孩兒口中</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="05b" n="11">아긔 이븨 흘러 드니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">阿孃十箇月 懷胎方乃降生</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">열리면 회 나니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">若是孝順之男 擎拳合掌而生</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">효옛 아 두 손 마초와 나되</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="3">不損阿孃</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="3">어미 해티 아녀 나고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="4">若是五逆之子 臂破阿孃胞胎</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="4">오역긔 아 어믜  헤티며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="5">手攀阿孃心肝</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="5">어믜 간 자브며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="6">脚踏阿孃胯骨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="6">어믜 도 박니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="7">敎孃如千刀撹腹 恰似萬刀攢心 如斯痛苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="7">어  갈로 딜워 기 시 알페 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06a" n="8">生得此身 猶如十恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06a" n="8">이 몸이 나믜 열 가짓 은니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">第一懷躭守護恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">처 여셔 몸 간슈 은니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="2">頌曰 累劫因緣重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">여러 겁 인연니 듕니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">今來托母胎</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">이저 와 어믜 예 드토다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="4">月逾生五臟</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="4">리 나므니 오장이 나고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="5">七七六精開</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="5">닐곱 리 되니 여 가지 이 여도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="6">體重如山岳</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="6">모미 므기워 뫼히 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="7">動止劫風尖</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="7">니믜 람믈 저허도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="8">羅衣都不掛</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="8">깁오 닙대 아니니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="06b" n="9">裝鏡惹塵埃</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="06b" n="9">겨우로예 듣그리  잇토다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">第二臨産受苦恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">둘채  니 슈고 은니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">頌曰 懷經十箇月 産難欲將臨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">여 열  디나니 나 시 님도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">朝朝如重病</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">아마다 므거운 병  고</sent><!-- ‘’은 ‘’의 오각으로 보임. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="4">日日似昏沉</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="4">날마다 혼침 도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="5">惶怖難成記</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="5">두리우미 그지업스며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="6">愁淚滿胷襟</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="6">눈므리 가믜 엿도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="7">含悲告親族</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="7">셜운 믈 머굼고 칭흐은 권당려 닐오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07a" n="8">惟戄死來侵</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07a" n="8">주글가 너거 저허노나</sent><!-- ‘거’는 ‘겨’의 탈획으로 보임. -->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="1">第三生子忘憂恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="1">세채 식 나니 시 니즌 은니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="2">頌曰 慈母生君日 五臟㧾開張</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="2">어미 식 나 나리 오이 다 여럿도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="3">身心俱悶絶</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="3">미 다 긔졀고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="4">血流似屠羊</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="4">피흘로미 양 다힌듯 도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="5">生已聞見健</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="5">나고 아기 건실타 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="6">歡喜倍加常</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="6">깃브미 더옥 도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="7">喜定悲還至</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="7">잇브미 경고 슬픈 미 도혀 나니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="07b" n="8">痛苦徹心腹</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="07b" n="8">설우미 간의 놋도다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">第四咽苦吐甘恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">네채  것 머겨셔  것 도여 머기 은</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">頌曰 父母恩深重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">부모이 은니 듕니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="3">恩憐無失時</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="3">이 그지업도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="4">吐甘無所息</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="4"> 거슬 토야 머기니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="5">咽苦不嚬眉</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="5"> 것 머글 제 긔디 아니도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="6">愛重情難忍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="6">랑이 듕니 졍을 디 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="7">恩深復倍悲</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="7">은니 기프니 다시 슬프고 셜우미 도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="8">但令孩子飽</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="8">아기  브르게 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08a" n="9">慈母不詞飢</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08a" n="9">어미 주려도 량 아니다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">第五廻乾就濕恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="1">다채 아기란   누이고 즌  눋 은</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="2">頌曰 母自身俱濕 將兒以就乾</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="2">어미   도라눕고 아기란   누이놋도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="3">兩乳充飢渴</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="3">두 져즈로 주리거든 머기고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="4">羅神掩風寒</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="4">깁소매로   둡놋도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="5">恩怜恒廢寢</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="5">어엿브니 미업고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="6">寵弄振能歡</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="6">괴노라니 즐겁도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="7">但令孩子穩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="7">다믄 아기 편안게 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="08b" n="8">慈母不求安</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="08b" n="8">어미 편안믈 구티 아니다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">第六乳哺養育恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">여슷채 졋 머겨 치 은니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="2">頌曰 慈母衆於地 嚴父配於天</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">어미 디 고 아비 하 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="3">覆載恩將等 父孃意亦然</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="3">은혜 부모와 가지로 다 믜여 아니니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="4">不憎無眼目</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="4">눈흘긘 저기 업고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="5">不嫌手足攣</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="5">혐의론 미 업니 손바리 니셧도디</sent><!-- ‘디’는 ‘다’의 오각으로 보임. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="6">誕腹親生子</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="6">친 식글 나니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09a" n="7">終日惜兼憐</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09a" n="7">져므두록 얏겨 니 어엿버 놋도다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="1">第七洗濁不淨恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="1">닐곱채 싯노라 니 조티 아니 은</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="2">頌曰 憶昔黃容質 姿媚甚豊濃</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="2">어믜  체 곱고 지뎌니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="3">眉分翠柳色</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="3">눈서븐 버들닙 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="4">兩臉奪蓮紅</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="4">두 귀미튼 년곳 더니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="5">恩深摧玉貌</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="5">식 기 은니 기프니 고온  사오나이 되오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="6">洗濁損盤龍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="6">싯노라 니 반룡어 슨도다</sent><!-- 쌍계사판에는 ‘반룡이 손도다’로 되어 있음. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="7">只爲憐男女</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="7">시글 랑노나 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="09b" n="8">慈母改顔容</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="09b" n="8">어뫼 양 도다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="1">第八遠行憶念恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="1">여듧 채 시기 나갓거든 렴 은</sent><!--여들ᄇ-->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="2">頌曰 死別誠難忍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="2">주거 여희믄 진실로 디 몯거니와</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="3">生離亦悲傷</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="3">사라셔 여희미 더옥 셜다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="4">子出開山外</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="4">아리 관산밧긔 나가시니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="5">母意在他鄕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="5">어믜 디 타의 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="6">日夜心相逐</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="6">일야의 미 서로 조차 잇고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="7">流淚數千行</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="7">눈므 일쳔 주리 흐놋다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="8">如猿泣愛子</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="8">나 식 랑홈 야</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10a" n="9">憶念斷肝腸</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10a" n="9">렴호 어 긋도다</sent><!-- ‘어’는 ‘애’의 오각으로 보임. -->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="1">第九爲造惡業恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="1">아홉채 모딘 일 진 은니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="2">頌曰 父母江山重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="2">부뫼 강산티 듕니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="3">深恩報實難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="3">은 가미 어렵도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="4">子苦願代受</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="4">시긔 슈고론 이 신어지라 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="5">兒勞母不安</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="5">분 어로 어미 편티 아녀놋다</sent><!-- 쌍계사판에는 ‘어로’가 ‘이’로 되어 있음. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="6">聞道遠行去</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="6">시기 머리 나가면</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="7">行遊夜臥寒</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="7">어미 바   누엇도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="8">男女暫辛苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="8">시기 잠간 신고여도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="10b" n="9">長使母心酸</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="10b" n="9">어미 믈 구치도다</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="1">第十究竟憐愍恩</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="1">열채 내죵을 각고 어엿버  은</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="2">頌曰 父母恩深重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="2">부모의 은니 듕니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="3">恩憐無失時</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="3">어엿버 일 시 업도라</sent><!-- ‘덥’은 ‘업’의 오각으로 보임. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="4">起座心相逐</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="4">안나 니나 미 서로 조찻고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="5">遠近意相隨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="5">머나 갓가오나 디 서로 조차 갓도다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="6">母年一百歲 常憂八十兒</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="6">어믜 나이 셰라도 상해 여니언 시글 시니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="7">欲知恩愛斷</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="7">으니 그초믈 알오쟈 면</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11a" n="8">命盡始分離</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11a" n="8">이 진야 여희니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="1">佛告阿難</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="1">부톄 아란려 니샤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="2">我觀衆生 雖紹人品</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="2">사미 비록 인뉴의 이시나</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="3">心行愚蒙</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="3">믄 어리니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="4">不思爺孃 有大恩德</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="4">부모의 큰 은더글 티 아니여</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="5">不生恭敬</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="5">공 믈 아니며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="11b" n="6">棄恩昔德 無有仁慈 不孝不義</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="11b" n="6">은 리며 더글 더디고 브효니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="1">阿孃 懷子十月之中</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="1">어미 식 여 열  이예</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="2">起坐不安</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="2">안나 니나 편티 아니어</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="3">如擎重擔</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="3">므거운 것 녠 며</sent><!-- 쌍계사판에는 ‘녠’이 아닌 ‘멘’으로 되어 있음. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="4">飮食不下</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="4">머근 거시 리디 아니여</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="5">如長病人</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="5"> 사 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a" n="6">月滿生時 受諸痛苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a" n="6">리 차 나 제 슈괴 그지 업고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12a-12b" n="7">須臾好惡 恐爲無常</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12a-12b" n="7">됴며 구조미 잠 이예 인니</sent><!--이^예-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="1">如殺猪羊</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="1"> 돋 다힌 듯야</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="2">血流遍地</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="2">피 흘러  펴디니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="3">受如是苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="3">슈괴 이러니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="4">生得此身 咽苦吐甘 抱持養育 洗濁不淨 不憚劬勞</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="4">푸머셔 기 제 믈 탄티 아니며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="5">忍熟忍寒</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="5">더위 며 치위 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="6">不詞辛苦</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="6">슈고뢰여도 슬흐여 아니니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="7">乾處兒臥 濕處母眠 三年之中 飮母白血</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="7">삼 년 이예 어믜  피 먹고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="8">孆孩童子 乃至盛年</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="8">라나거든</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="9">將敎禮義 婚嫁官學</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="9">녜도 치며 혼인며 글 라치며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="10">備求資業 携賀艱辛</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="10">여러 가짓 일 초와 신고호</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="11">懃苦之終 不言恩絶</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="11">내죵의 은 니디 아니니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="12">男女有病 父母病生</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="12">시기 면 부뫼 이 나니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="13">子若病愈 慈母方差</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="13">그 이 됴케 부모도 편니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="12b" n="14">如斯養育 願早成人</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="12b" n="14">이러시 쳐일 사되와댜 원니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13a" n="1">及其長成 返爲不孝</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13a" n="1">라나면 도혀 브효니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13a-13b" n="2">尊親共語 應對慃[忄+夅] 拗眼戾情</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13a-13b" n="2">얼우 마 거스려 답며</sent><!-- ^ 거-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="1">欺凌伯叔</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="1">족도 소겨 업시위 너기머</sent><!-- ‘머’는 ‘며’에서 탈획한 것으로 보임. -->
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="2">打罵兄弟</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="2">도 티며 구짓고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="3">毁辱親情 無有禮義</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="3">어버도 슈욕야 녜되 업스니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="4">不遵師範</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="4">스의 버블 좃디 아니놋다</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="5">父母敎令 久不依從</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="5">부모의 교도 의티 아니며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="6">兄弟共言 故相拗戾</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="6">뎨의 말도 서 거스리고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="7">出入往來 不啓尊人</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="7">나드리 제 얼운려 니디 아니코</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="8">言行高踈 擅意爲事</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="8">말솜과 시리 서재여 제 도로 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="9">父母訓罰 伯叔語非 童幼憐愍 尊人遮護</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="9">부뫼 치고 얼운니 뒤덥거든</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="10">漸漸長成 狼戾不調 不伏虧爲</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="10">졈졈 라면 거스려 화동티 아니여</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="11">返生嗔恨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="11">도혀 셕 내니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="12">棄際親友</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="12">친 버드란 리고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="13">朋附惡人</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="13">모딘 사믈 조차</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="14">習已性成</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="14">습이 되어</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b" n="15">遂爲强計</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b" n="15">모딘 계교 니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="13b-14a" n="16">被人誘進 逃竄他鄕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="13b-14a" n="16">미 달애여든 타의 나가</sent><!--^미-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14a" n="1">遠背爺孃 離家別貫 或因經紀 或爲征行</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14a" n="1">부모도 려며 집도 여희오</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14a" n="2">荏苒因循 便爲婚娶</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14a" n="2">여러  디나면 겨집야</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14a" n="3">由斯留碍 久不還家</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14a" n="3">오래 드러 오디 아니니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="1">或在他鄕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="1"> 타의 가셔</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="2">不能謹愼/</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="2">조심티 몯야</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="3">被人謀點 橫事句牽</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="3"> 예 감겨 그 니다가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="4">枉被刑責 牢獄枷鎖</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="4">죄 니버 옥긔 가티며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="5">或遭病患 尼難縈纏 困苦飢羸 無人看侍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="5">야 주려도 간슈리 업스면</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="6">被他嫌賤</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="6">미 쳔히 너겨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="7">倚棄街衢</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="7">거리예 더디니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="8">因此命終 無人救療</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="8">인여 주거도 구의리 업서</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="9">膨脹爛壞</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="9">오장이 서거</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="10">日曝風吹</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="10">볃며 람 불여</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="11">白骨漂零 寄他鄕土</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="11">  타의 가 려시면</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="12">便與親族 歡會長乖</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="12">아과 디 노로미 어긔여 디고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="13">父母心隨 永懷憂念</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="13">부모의 믄  렴야</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="14">或因啼泣 眼闇目盲</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="14">혹 우다가 눈 멀며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="15">或爲悲哀 氣咽成病</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="15">혹 셜워 샹심이 되며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="16">或緣憶子 襄變死亡 作鬼暴魂</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="16">혹 주거 호니 되어도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="14b" n="17">不曾割捨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="14b" n="17">닛디 아니니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="1">或復聞子 不崇孝義</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="1"> 효도란 아니코</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="2">朋遂異端</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="2">다 사오나온 이 조며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="3">無賴麤頑 好習無益</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="3">쇽졀업슨 이 화</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="4">鬪打竊盜</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="4">싸흠며 도다가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="5">觸犯鄕閭 飮酒樗滿 奸非過失</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="5"> 죄 니브며 왼 일 지서</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="6">帶累兄弟</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="6">동도 더러이며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="7">惱亂爺孃</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="7">부모도 심케 니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="8">晨去暮還 尊親憂念</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="8">새배 나가 나죄 드러와</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="9">不知父母 動止寒溫</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="9">부모의 치우며 더운 줄도 모며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a" n="10">晦朔朝晡 永垂扶侍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a" n="10">  뫼셔시미  어긔니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15a-15b" n="11">父母年邁 形貌衰嬴</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15a-15b" n="11">무뫼 나히 드러  사오나이 되면</sent><!--드^러-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15b" n="1">羞恥見人 嗔呵欺抑</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15b" n="1"> 뵈디 붓그려 구짓고 소기니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15b" n="2">或復父孤母寡 獨守空堂</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15b" n="2"> 홀아비나 홀어미나 혼자 뷘 지븨 잇거든</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15b" n="3">猶若客人 寄住他舍</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15b" n="3">손티 너겨 다 지븨 가 살며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="15b-16a" n="4">床席塵土 拂拭無時</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="15b-16a" n="4">좌의 듣글도 디 아니며</sent><!--글^도-->

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="1">參問起居 從斯斷絶</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="1">안부도 묻디 아니며</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="2">寒溫飢渴 曾不聞知</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="2"> 골코  라도 모고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="3">晝夜恒常 自嗟自嘆</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="3">나지나 바미나 탄니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="4">應賫饌物 供養尊親 每詐羞慙</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="4">머글것 다가 어버시 머기 붓그레 너기니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="5">異人怪笑</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="5"> 슈샹히 너겨 웃니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="6">或持時食 供給妻兒 醜拙疲勞 無避羞恥</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="6">쳐식 머기믄 더럽고 바도 붓그려 아니니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="7">妻妾約束 每事依從</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="7">겨지븨 말란 아 일도 의고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16a" n="8">尊者嗔喝 全無畏懼</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16a" n="8">얼우 지럼믄 젼혀 저티 아니니라</sent>

<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="1">或復是女 通配他人 未家之時 咸皆孝順</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="1">  시기 미가여셔 다 효도다가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="2">婚嫁已訖 不孝遂增</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="2">혼인 후의 브효니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="3">父母微嗔</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="3">부모 잠 구지지도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="4">卽生怨恨</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="4">노여 고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="5">夫婿打罵</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="5">남지 티고 구지저도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="6">忍秀甘心</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="6">고 감심히 너기니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="7">異姓他宗 情深眷重</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="7">싀권으란 그지업시 접고</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="8">自家骨肉 却已爲踈</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="8">제 녁 권으란 소히 니</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="9">或隨夫壻 外郡他鄕</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="9"> 남진 조차 다 골 가</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b" n="10">離別爺孃</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="kor" page="16b" n="10">부모 여히여도</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="16b-17a" n="11">無心戀慕</sent>
